489
00:28:44.252 --> 00:28:45.191
All right. Thank you.

490
00:28:45.532 --> 00:28:47.592
Yeah.

491
00:28:47.692 --> 00:28:48.892
Excellent work. Thank you.

492
00:28:49.652 --> 00:28:49.912
Thank you.

493
00:28:57.552 --> 00:29:01.192
Hi. So we are excited to go to our next talk.

