00:41:21.136 --> 00:41:23.246
Sorry, I think I meant like, I know it's really difficult and-

703
00:41:23.296 --> 00:41:24.056
Yeah, sorry. I didn't--

704
00:41:24.456 --> 00:41:26.806
It's like an embryonic stage. Like-

705
00:41:26.856 --> 00:41:27.916
Oh, embryonic stage.

706
00:41:27.946 --> 00:41:27.946
