1348
01:18:27.804 --> 01:18:30.264
So, HHH is a life-threatening

1349
01:18:30.924 --> 01:18:34.584
hyperinflammatory syndrome caused by the dysregulation of the

1350
01:18:35.044 --> 01:18:36.784
