1351
01:18:37.584 --> 01:18:41.184
and it is generally categorized into the primary or secondary HHH.

1352
01:18:42.084 --> 01:18:45.824
So primary HHH is a pediatric genetic disease

1353
01:18:45.944 --> 01:18:49.904
caused by the defect in the lymphocytes function, such as

1354
01:18:49.944 --> 01:18:53.124
pyferrin or UNC13D, STX11 or

1355
01:18:53.244 --> 01:18:54.064
STSBP2.

1356
01:18:54.924 --> 01:18:58.844
In contrast, secondary HHH occurs in adults, and it

1357
01:18:58.904 --> 01:19:02.444
