1358
01:19:03.184 --> 01:19:07.174
So when we look at the causes of the secondary HHH, about 30% of the

1359
01:19:07.264 --> 01:19:11.144
secondary HHH is caused by the hematologic malignancies such

1360
01:19:11.184 --> 01:19:15.044
as lymphoma or leukemia. However, the solid tumor proportion is very

1361
01:19:15.064 --> 01:19:17.324
low, so it is very distinct phenotype.

1362
01:19:19.184 --> 01:19:23.064
However, the pathophysiology of the secondary HHH is less

1363
01:19:23.104 --> 01:19:27.000
understood.And recently, with the advent of the CAR T cells

1364
01:19:27.040 --> 01:19:30.400
or bispecific antibody therapies, we acknowledge that the

1365
01:19:30.420 --> 01:19:34.020
