1375
01:20:06.170 --> 01:20:09.980
And without treatment, the median survival was less than one month.

1376
01:20:10.500 --> 01:20:14.380
And I also saw a patient with the secondary HHH, a patient

1377
01:20:14.580 --> 01:20:18.560
who suffered from the lymphoma-associated cases, but the

1378
01:20:18.760 --> 01:20:22.060
